do it fast!

01:58:37.360 --> 01:58:40.195
Hicks!
Go!
Come on. Let's go.

01:58:41.865 --> 01:58:43.365
Move!

01:58:50.331 --> 01:58:53.834
Which way is it to
the landing field from here?
This way.

01:58:56.379 --> 01:58:58.338
[Aliens Shrieking ]

01:58:58.423 --> 01:59:01.258
[ Newt ]
Go right.

01:59:03.511 --> 01:59:05.471
This way. This way.

